{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Varyana launches three harpoons ahead of her, piercing enemies for {if:SF_10}{c_number}{payload:PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}heavy{/if} Physical damage. She then rips them back, Pulling In and Stunning enemies for {c_number}{SF_1}{/c} seconds.
